. This social network analysis could also be done for a Sector\nInnovation System, and we do so for Nanotech to determine empirically the\nknowledge field relevant for this emerging scientific domain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2011 18:21:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-02"}
