ation on mass and\nangular momentum transfer processes in binary stars. Here we show examples of\nfour PNe for which we have discovered their binary nature, including the\ndiscovery of a rare case of a barium-rich cool central star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2011 19:04:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Aug 2011 17:30:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-08"}
